OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,FReporter Gregg Easteal has been at
OL,7,FNewcastle Crown Court where XL Bully
OL,8,Fowner Christopher Bell was sentenced
OL,10,FThe owner of an XL Bully dog which
OL,11,Fsavaged a man to death has been jailed
OL,12,Ffor three years.
OL,14,FChristopher Bell, 45, previously
OL,15,Fadmitted being the owner of a dog
OL,16,Fwhich caused injury leading to death
OL,17,Fwhile dangerously out of control in a
OL,18,Fpublic place.
