OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,FIan Langley, 54, was walking his puppy
OL,7,Fin Shiney Row, near Sunderland, when
OL,8,Fhe was attacked by a dog and suffered
OL,9,Ffatal neck injuries on 3 October 2023.
OL,11,FAt Newcastle Crown Court on Monday (27
OL,12,FJanuary), Bell, who now lives in Hull,
OL,13,Fwas sentenced to three years in prison
OL,14,Fand was banned from keeping dogs.
OL,16,FFollowing the smashing of a window at
OL,17,Fhis home, Bell had run from his
OL,18,Faddress with his two dogs to chase Mr
OL,19,FLangley, who he thought to be
OL,20,Fresponsible.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
