OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,FAfter a short pursuit, one of Bell's
OL,7,Fdogs, named Titan and described in the
OL,8,Fcharge as "an American bully XL",
OL,9,Fgrabbed Mr Langley by the throat and
OL,10,Fcaused catastrophic injuries.
OL,12,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,13,Fsaid he died a short time later after
OL,14,Flosing a significant amount of blood.
OL,16,FPolice shot the dog at the scene to
OL,17,Fprotect the public and it was
OL,18,Funderstood at the time of the attack
OL,19,Fthat another XL bully was taken away
OL,20,Fby police for public safety.
