OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,FNeighbours said Mr Langley, who was
OL,7,Foriginally from Liverpool, was walking
OL,8,Fhis Patterdale puppy called Bow when
OL,9,Fhe was attacked.
OL,11,FHis puppy bolted and managed to escape
OL,12,Fand was being looked after by a
OL,13,Fneighbour in the aftermath of the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FTracey, one of Ian Langley's
OL,17,Fneighbours, told ITV Tyne Tees he was
OL,18,F'covered in blood' and couldn't talk
OL,19,Fas she paid tribute to him
