OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,FOne of Mr Langley's neighbours,
OL,7,FTracey, told ITV Tyne Tees that she
OL,8,Foffered first aid before paramedics
OL,9,Farrived.
OL,11,FRecalling the attack, she said: "Two
OL,12,Fof my children heard a scream and then
OL,13,FI went out, I knew instantly who it
OL,14,Fwas, he got up and walked towards me.
OL,16,F"He was covered from the neck down in
OL,17,Fblood. He couldn't talk, he was just
OL,18,Fgargling. I made him sit down and I
OL,19,Fput pressure on his neck.
