OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,F"I was just talking to him, when
OL,7,Fsomebody is in that predicament you
OL,8,Fjust want to remind them of something
OL,9,Fso I was talking about his son.
OL,11,F"I've known him for years. He was a
OL,12,Fproud dad and a lovely lad, he never
OL,13,Fharmed anybody."
OL,15,FSince the attack, and following a
OL,16,Fnumber of other attacks by XL Bully
OL,17,Fdogs around the country, the breed is
OL,18,Fnow banned in this country.
