OL,3,CXL Bully owner jailed for three years
OL,4,Cafter dog savaged man to death
OL,6,FSince February 2024 it has been a
OL,7,Fcriminal offence to own an XL Bully
OL,8,Fwithout an exemption certificate.
OL,10,FThe dogs must also be kept on a lead
OL,11,Fand muzzled in public places, as well
OL,12,Fas neutered.
